Document: OpenXRActionMap
Path: godot/classes/class_openxractionmap.rst
Summary: Defines mappings between OpenXR actions and input events.

OpenXRActionMap

Inherits: Resource < RefCounted < Object

This class defines mappings between OpenXR actions and input events. It allows you to configure how physical input from VR controllers is translated into logical actions within your Godot project using the OpenXR plugin. You can define actions, bind them to specific controller inputs, and specify how these actions should be represented as Godot input events. This is crucial for creating cross-platform VR experiences that respond correctly to various VR hardware.
