Path: godot/classes/class_openxractionmap.rst
Summary: Defines methods for managing OpenXR action sets and interaction profiles.

Method: add_action_set(action_set: OpenXRActionSet) → void
Adds an action set to the map.

Method: add_interaction_profile(interaction_profile: OpenXRInteractionProfile) → void
Adds an interaction profile to the map.

Method: create_default_action_sets() → void
Creates default action sets for common XR functionalities.

Method: find_action_set(name: String) → OpenXRActionSet |const|
Finds an action set by its name. Returns null if not found.

Method: find_interaction_profile(name: String) → OpenXRInteractionProfile |const|
Finds an interaction profile by its name. Returns null if not found.

Method: get_action_set(idx: int) → OpenXRActionSet |const|
Retrieves an action set at the specified index.

Method: get_action_set_count() → int |const|
Returns the total number of action sets in the map.

Method: get_interaction_profile(idx: int) → OpenXRInteractionProfile |const|
Retrieves an interaction profile at the specified index.

Method: get_interaction_profile_count() → int |const|
Returns the total number of interaction profiles in the map.

Method: remove_action_set(action_set: OpenXRActionSet) → void
Removes an action set from the map.

Method: remove_interaction_profile(interaction_profile: OpenXRInteractionProfile) → void
Removes an interaction profile from the map.
